<p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-AU style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-AU'>M=
any of the
settings of this mod can be set by the player in the BaconSettings.txt file.
Feel free to change and adjust as you see fit.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-AU style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-AU'>N=
ote: All
references to settings refer to BaconSettings.txt file.<o:p></o:p></span></=
p>

