EN-AU
style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-AU'>Crew experience levels</span></b><span
lang=3DEN-AU style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-AU'>: Crew gain experience when
inflicting damage (and can lose it if they take too much damage). View with
Ctrl-s. Each level above &#8220;Green&#8221; gives a random bonus to the sh=
ip.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

